{"prompt": "Generate a website for a real estate brokerage. The website should be futuristic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Astro Realty</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #ff0000;\n            --secondary-color: #e60000;\n            --background-color: #0d0d0d;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --accent-color: #f0f0f0;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 3px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1920x1080/0d0d0d/ffffff?text=Futuristic+Cityscape') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(13, 13, 13, 0.8) 0%, rgba(13, 13, 13, 0) 100%);\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content h2 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero-content p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border: 2px solid var(--brand-color);\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        .properties-section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n        }\n\n        .properties-section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .property-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .property-card {\n            background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .property-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .property-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .property-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .property-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .property-info p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #bbb;\n        }\n\n        .property-price {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: linear-gradient(to left, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            box-shadow: 0 -4px 15px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>ASTRO REALTY</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#properties\">Properties</a>\n                <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Discover Your Future Home</h2>\n            <p>Innovative living, unparalleled style.</p>\n            <a href=\"#properties\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Listings</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"properties\" class=\"properties-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Featured Properties</h2>\n            <div class=\"property-grid\">\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/1a1a1a/ffffff?text=Luxury+Penthouse\" alt=\"Luxury Penthouse\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Celestial Penthouse</h3>\n                        <p>3 Bedrooms | 2 Bathrooms | Panoramic City Views</p>\n                        <p class=\"property-price\">$2,500,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/1a1a1a/ffffff?text=Modern+Villa\" alt=\"Modern Villa\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Quantum Villa</h3>\n                        <p>4 Bedrooms | 3 Bathrooms | Smart Home Integration</p>\n                        <p class=\"property-price\">$1,800,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/1a1a1a/ffffff?text=Urban+Loft\" alt=\"Urban Loft\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h3>Nebula Loft</h3>\n                        <p>2 Bedrooms | 2 Bathrooms | Industrial Chic Design</p>\n                        <p class=\"property-price\">$950,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"properties-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Astro Realty</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">\n                Astro Realty is at the forefront of futuristic real estate, connecting clients with properties that redefine modern living. We leverage cutting-edge technology and visionary design to deliver exceptional experiences and unparalleled value. Our mission is to make the dream of owning a futuristic home a tangible reality.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"properties-section\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0;\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em;\">\n                Ready to explore the future of real estate? Contact us today.\n            </p>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em; margin-top: 10px;\">\n                Email: <a href=\"mailto:contact@astrorealty.com\" style=\"color: var(--brand-color);\">contact@astrorealty.com</a> | Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2077 Astro Realty. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}